          <td height="45" VALIGN="TOP" bgcolor="#333333"><div class="topictitle"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>
      <tr>
       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">The Safehouse E3 Vanguard Report: Part 5</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nenjin Darkeyes</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">May 27, 2005, 18:19</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=The%20Safehouse%20E3%20Vanguard%20Report%3A%20Part%205&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_14.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/reviews/printer_14.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	  <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/articles/exec/goforum.cgi?id=14&cat=19">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
